[SISTER] Thank you.

45
00:03:56,208 --> 00:03:57,583
[BROTHER] Let's go.

46
00:03:57,666 --> 00:03:59,875
[AKENO] Be careful
crossing the street.

47
00:04:01,666 --> 00:04:04,125
[AKENO] A brother's love, huh.

48
00:04:04,583 --> 00:04:07,333
[school bells chime]

49
