play to Sun Seto.

57
00:04:23,250 --> 00:04:25,666
[AKENO] Is that correct?
Are you the one who taught her?

58
00:04:26,458 --> 00:04:27,708
It's true. I did.

59
00:04:27,791 --> 00:04:29,708
Well, I guess
that explains it.

60
00:04:30,041 --> 00:04:32,458
[NAGASUMI THINKS] Now I know why
Sun's such a great swordsman!

61
00:04:32,541 --> 00:04:35,083
No wonder she could
fight Akeno to a stalemate!

62
00:04:35,625 --> 00:04:38,500
Wow, you taught her
