[NAGASUMI] Then that
means you have amnesia!

72
00:04:57,625 --> 00:05:00,750
Yes... So my life before
I joined the Seto gang?

73
00:05:00,833 --> 00:05:03,750
Sorry, but I just
can't remember.

74
00:05:03,833 --> 00:05:06,875
I'm so sorry, Masa.
No one ever told me that.

75
00:05:06,958 --> 00:05:08,791
It's a surprise
to me, too.

76
00:05:09,291 --> 00:05:11,458
[AKENO] Amnesia? How vexing!

77
00:05:11,541 --> 00:05:12,833
Are ya okay?

78
00:05:12,916 --> 00:05:15,166
Does this have something
to do with Sun's sword play?

79
00:05:15,250 --> 00:05:16,458
Her swordsmanship is without

80
