a doubt that of
the Shiranui school.

81
00:05:18,625 --> 00:05:20,958
A style passed
down through my family!

82
00:05:21,041 --> 00:05:22,916
[SUN] Really? Wow,
what a coincidence.

83
00:05:23,000 --> 00:05:25,291
At least learn the name
of your own sword style, Sun.

84
00:05:25,375 --> 00:05:26,458
[SUN] Yes!

85
00:05:26,541 --> 00:05:27,791
Wait, why would
you know the

86
00:05:27,875 --> 00:05:30,083
sword style passed down
through Akeno's family?

87
00:05:30,166 --> 00:05:31,458
[AKENO] Once...

88
00:05:31,541 --> 00:05:32,791
I had a brother, one who

89
00:05:32,875 --> 00:05:35,458
