older than I was.

90
00:05:35,833 --> 00:05:37,083
[AKENO] He was a
master swordsman,

91
00:05:37,166 --> 00:05:38,833
and as the heir to the family,

92
00:05:38,916 --> 00:05:41,916
he was charged with being lead
examiner for the Mermaid Exam.

93
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:45,166
Even though I was young,
I was so proud of my brother.

94
00:05:46,291 --> 00:05:47,708
But...

95
00:05:47,791 --> 00:05:50,666
...we suddenly lost all contact
with him during a mission.

96
00:05:52,791 --> 00:05:54,416
[YOUNG AKENO] Big brother!

97
00:05:55,666 --> 00:05:57,541
He was on assignment
in the Inland Sea,

98
00:05:57,625 --> 00:06:00,333
and he was there to evaluate
your outfit, the Seto gang!

99
00:06:00,416 --> 00:06:01,375
You!

100
00:06:01,458 --> 00:06:03,625
I didn't know that
missy. I'm sorry.

101
00:06:03,708 --> 00:06:05,083
[AKENO] The one who
taught you that sword

102
00:06:05,166 --> 00:06:06,708
style must have been my brother!

103
00:06:06,791 --> 00:06:08,375
That means you might
be the only person with

104
00:06:08,458 --> 00:06:11,041
a clue as to what
happened to him, but...

105
00:06:11,125 --> 00:06:12,583
...you have amnesia.

106
00:06:13,041 --> 00:06:14,208
Your big brother.

107
00:06:14,291 --> 00:06:16,958
Ya really do wanna see
him again, huh, Akkie?

108
00:06:17,041 --> 00:06:18,875
[AKENO] I do, and if I
actually find that

109
00:06:18,958 --> 00:06:21,041
shameless coward
alive somewhere,

110
00:06:21,125 --> 00:06:23,833
he won't be living for much
longer because I'll kill 'em!

111
00:06:23,916 --> 00:06:25,041
[NAGASUMI] Huh?

112
00:06:25,125 --> 00:06:26,125
[AKENO] That brother
of mine is the only blot

113
00:06:26,208 --> 00:06:27,208
on the record of
the Shiranui family...

114
00:06:27,291 --> 00:06:28,708
[NAGASUMI]
Stop, you're scaring me,

115
00:06:28,791 --> 00:06:30,458
and don't you think you're
being a little hard on the guy?

116
00:06:30,541 --> 00:06:32,625
[AKENO] He abandoned
his mission and disappeared!

117
00:06:32,708 --> 00:06:34,916
He's a disgrace to mermaid
officials everywhere!

118
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:36,916
He's a shameful,
despicable criminal!

119
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:38,166
And both the government
and my family have...

120
00:06:38,250 --> 00:06:40,666
[SUN] Wow, things got
violent really quick.

121
