[GOZABURO] Oh, man,
this is bad. Really bad!

122
00:06:43,958 --> 00:06:46,041
[AKENO] Masa, even the smallest
clue might be of some help.

123
00:06:46,125 --> 00:06:48,083
Do you remember anything at all?

124
00:06:48,166 --> 00:06:50,041
Not really, no.

125
00:06:50,125 --> 00:06:53,041
Just about everything's
a blank, but...

126
00:06:53,125 --> 00:06:54,500
[SUN] But what?

127
00:06:54,583 --> 00:06:57,083
[MASA] Well, for some reason
I recall liking swordplay.

128
00:06:57,166 --> 00:06:58,583
In fact, I taught
it to Miss Sun as

129
00:06:58,666 --> 00:07:00,791
much for my own
sake as for hers.

130
00:07:00,875 --> 00:07:03,166
It does something
for me, you know?

131
00:07:03,250 --> 00:07:06,541
Whenever I hold a sword,
my head starts to clear.

132
00:07:06,625 --> 00:07:08,958
And I start to feel like I
might remember something.

133
00:07:09,041 --> 00:07:10,291
Okay, if that's the case,

134
00:07:10,375 --> 00:07:12,541
do ya wanna go to the
kendo hall behind the gym?

135
00:07:12,625 --> 00:07:14,666
Huh? What's that? Kendo?

136
00:07:14,750 --> 00:07:15,708
Well, yeah!

137
00:07:15,791 --> 00:07:16,708
Because ya might
remember somethin'

138
00:07:16,791 --> 00:07:18,041
