141
00:07:21,416 --> 00:07:23,958
Well, let's go, Nagasumi!
What the--

142
00:07:24,041 --> 00:07:25,208
[NAGASUMI MACHINE] No one
can come to the phone right now.

143
00:07:25,291 --> 00:07:26,583
[SUN] Nagasumi?

144
00:07:26,666 --> 00:07:28,333
[GOZABURO]
Would ya stop squirmin'?

145
00:07:28,416 --> 00:07:29,750
Now listen up, maggot!

146
00:07:29,833 --> 00:07:31,000
Um, Sun's Dad!

147
00:07:31,083 --> 00:07:32,291
What the heck are you doing?

148
00:07:32,375 --> 00:07:33,666
Ya gotta get
Sun and Akeno

149
00:07:33,750 --> 00:07:35,000
away from Masa now!

150
00:07:35,083 --> 00:07:36,291
[NAGASUMI] Oh really why?

151
00:07:36,375 --> 00:07:38,750
I'll tell ya, but ya gotta
cooperate with me!

152
00:07:38,833 --> 00:07:40,458
[NAGASUMI]
In that case, never mind!

153
00:07:40,541 --> 00:07:42,625
Ya see maggot,
it all began ten years ago.

154
00:07:42,708 --> 00:07:44,541
[NAGASUMI]
I told you I don't want to know!

155
00:07:46,083 --> 00:07:48,166
Goldfish? Goldfish?

156
00:07:50,666 --> 00:07:52,250
(hiccup)

157
