[GOZABURO] Hey, it's you.

159
00:07:57,500 --> 00:07:59,416
How come ya ain't
drinkin' any sake?

160
00:07:59,500 --> 00:08:02,458
Hey, come on, officials
can have fun, too, right?

161
00:08:02,541 --> 00:08:04,416
We can and do,
but it's frowned upon

162
00:08:04,500 --> 00:08:06,083
