behave myself and abstain.

165
00:08:10,250 --> 00:08:11,625
Hey, hold on there!

166
00:08:11,708 --> 00:08:14,291
Ya came all the way
out here to Seto to visit us!

167
00:08:14,375 --> 00:08:15,666
We can't just send
ya home without

168
00:08:15,750 --> 00:08:18,541
experiencin' some
of our hospitality.

169
00:08:18,625 --> 00:08:20,166
[GOZABURO] Come sit down
and have a drink with me!

170
00:08:20,250 --> 00:08:21,541
I insist!

171
00:08:21,625 --> 00:08:24,333
[AKENO'S BROTHER] I shouldn't...
But, if you insist.

172
00:08:26,333 --> 00:08:28,250
[Gozaburo laughs]

173
00:08:28,333 --> 00:08:30,166
Yeah! Would ya
look at her go!

174
00:08:30,250 --> 00:08:32,000
Ain't my little
girl adorable?

175
00:08:32,083 --> 00:08:33,833
[AKENO'S BROTHER]
Her name is Sun, Right?

176
00:08:34,916 --> 00:08:37,208
You're very proud
of her, aren't you?

177
00:08:37,958 --> 00:08:41,083
Yeah, I sure am... And
fer the rest of her life,

178
00:08:41,166 --> 00:08:42,500
I gonna protect her!

179
00:08:42,583 --> 00:08:45,166
