life, huh? Well...

180
00:08:45,250 --> 00:08:47,791
I guess her future husband will
be in for a rough time then.

181
00:08:47,875 --> 00:08:49,375
Huh?

182
00:08:49,833 --> 00:08:52,416
What? Husband? Uh...

183
00:08:53,583 --> 00:08:54,583
[GOZABURO]
Future husband, my ass!

184
00:08:54,666 --> 00:08:56,500
Um, no, look, Mr. Seto...

185
00:08:56,583 --> 00:08:57,958
[GOZABURO] And if any
maggots try put their

186
00:08:58,041 --> 00:08:59,791
